title: It’s not your imagination: Shopping on Amazon has gotten worse
description: Most of what you see at first on Amazon is now an ad.

title: Apple executive defends multibillion-dollar Google deal at trial
description: Eddy Cue’s testimony at the Google antitrust trial gave a rare peek into negotiations between the two tech giants that set Google as the default search engine for Apple devices.

title: What just happened to Amazon? The FTC’s antitrust lawsuit, explained.
description: Here’s why the United States government says Amazon is an illegal monopoly and how the lawsuit could change shopping on Amazon.

title: U.S., 17 states sue Amazon alleging monopolistic practices led to higher prices
description: The Federal Trade Commission and 17 state attorneys general allege Amazon abused its powers to raise prices and levy high fees in sweeping antitrust lawsuit.

title: The iPhone 15’s hidden cost: Photos fill up your storage much faster
description: Apple’s new iPhone takes photos that are about 65 percent larger than older iPhones. You could end up spending more to store them in iCloud.
